{"tid":1791424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美林邨女子伏屍大廈對開","createTime":"2019-12-20T20:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T00:15:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1e9ce73b07fb335c935311f31213dcf303d7599","tid":1791424,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T20:06:10.000Z","msg":"沙田美林邨美槐樓，下午5時許，街坊報案指發現一名女子倒卧大廈對開，救護員到場經檢驗證實女子已氣絕身亡。警員接報到場，用帳篷將屍體蓋上，初步懷疑女子由高處墮下，正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後表示，事主36歲姓曾，於現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事主從上址一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。"},{"pid":"4b4ea7b56751b99f42f721d8ecf8bb376cf55fa6","tid":1791424,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T20:06:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191220/60401017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60401017&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQahYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=18e16df0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60401017&h=5c59eef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191220/60401017</a>"},{"pid":"70b9cea7543f23375d888951d2fd512241fd4b99","tid":1791424,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T23:39:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無可疑</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6a063f84dc8965bbd0aaf736f141b04085d6ab6d","tid":1791424,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T23:42:44.000Z","msg":"有冇遺書 有冇全裸 有冇傷痕 一論冇可疑 咁點先有可疑呀 只要你係少年青年或著全黑就有可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5482279121ec66082f54a725cb9b7ecc3f036715","tid":1791424,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddf1d479662ac1c5043f26423194484